fsb.config.avatars.tooltip: What will be used download/upload avatars
fsb.config.pings.tooltip: What will be used to send/receive pings
fsb.config.sync.tooltip:
Sync pings will use "Ping priority" value, unless "Figura + FSB" is selected, because sync can't be done with both Figura and FSB
This setting determines what has higher priority
fsb.config.sync.1.tooltip: Figura backend has higher priority for sync
fsb.config.sync.2.tooltip: FSB has higher priority for sync
fsb.config.priority.1.tooltip: Uses only Figura's backend for this setting
fsb.config.priority.2.tooltip: Uses Figura's backend if connected to, otherwise trying to use FSB
fsb.config.priority.3.tooltip: Uses both Figura's backend and FSB
fsb.config.priority.4.tooltip: Uses FSB if server has it, otherwise trying to use Figura's backend
fsb.config.priority.5.tooltip: Uses only FSB for this setting
